text: My husband loves pizza, he could eat it every day.. I on the other hand can't handle all of that grease and usually get stomachaches from eating pizza. Pie Five Pizza was a different story. The toppings and the crust were so fresh and there …More

text: A new favorite quick lunch place for us. On Mondays the $5.55 pizza can't be beat. Otherwise, $7.99 for an 11 inch pizza is a good price, too. The thin crust was perfectly crispy & the toppings  were loaded on. Beer & wine is available in addition to sweet & unsweetened teas & Coke products.

It was delish, highly recommend adding ricotta it was a generous portion and very well baked! I am usually not such a pizza lover; however I think I have become a regular!
